        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
            <p>Not published before <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>132400</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"><certainty locus="name" match=".."/></gap>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested"><name nymRef="#_ς"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><seg part="F">ς</seg></name></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#_ιππος" type="patronymic"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><seg part="F"><supplied reason="lost">ί</supplied><unclear>π</unclear>π<unclear>ω</unclear></seg></name></persName>
                    <lb n="3"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#_ις"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><seg part="F">ις</seg></name></persName>
                    <lb n="3a"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"><certainty locus="name" match=".."/></gap>
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>s fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ippos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>is <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>s son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ippos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>is <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>s figlio di <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ippos, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>is <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
               <p>This very fragmentary block is not very rewarding. The very tender local limestone, exposed to the action of wind and salt, is a very 
               bad support for inscriptions. The fist letter at line 1 was perhaps a much eroded eta. The third line may have been added later on, as its 
               sigma differs notably from that at line 1.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
